{"tid":1984573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動Post] 真香港五一黃金週 五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T03:33:38.000Z","uid":11870,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"b651d956a12fadbbd3ae4976d496d2e58afff4a1","tid":1984573,"uid":11870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAkEO9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAkEO9p.jpg&h=4c6c3559&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>簡介</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n往年，大家對🖐☝️黃金週嘅印象就係大量中国人到香港消費，受益嘅只有奢侈品商店。試問，呢種消費模式係香港需要的嗎? 我相信，大家都唔會認為係需要嘅。<br />\n<br />\n所以，今個 🖐☝️黃金週係改變呢個現象嘅好機會。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日，喺武漢肺炎同港共政府雙重打擊之下，市道越黎越差，各行各業進入咗寒冬期。 雖然我哋有黃色經濟圈，但係，宜家大家因爲疫情關係，減少外出，各行各業的黃色商店生意大減，苦不堪言。喺過去兩個月，有部份黃店因虧蝕過多而被迫結業。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我哋香港人更應該團結起來，喺🖐☝️黃金週振興黃色經濟圈，大量幫襯黃店，務求令一眾黃店度過這段寒冬期。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我哋香港人亦應大量設計🖐☝️黃金週文宣，嘗試以量取勝，令香港人一見到🖐☝️黃金週，就會聯想起「五大訴求，缺一不可」。同時，中国人亦會玻璃心發作，而對🖐☝️黃金週感到極抗拒，從而光復🖐☝️黃金週。<br />\n<br />\n更多資訊請去 TG@ HKGoldenWeek<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n活動另外一個部份係騎劫 🖐☝️黃金週<br />\n<br />\n當大家諗起🖐☝️黃金週，我相信，大家都會諗起中国人嘅🖐☝️黃金週假期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。每一年🖐☝️黃金週都會有大量中国人入侵香港。<br />\n<br />\n所以，係今年，我地要去騎劫🖐☝️黃金週 將佢變成🖐☝️黃金週，等人一見到 🖐☝️黃金週，就會諗起 五大訴求 缺一不可!<br />\n<br />\n而呢個計劃會有三個戰場，分別係本地戰線，外國戰線，以及牆內戰線。<br />\n<br />\n首先，喺本地戰線，文宣手足可以大量設計🖐☝️黃金週文宣，嘗試以量取勝 。另外，手足們亦應多加善用文宣手足的設計，將這些設計大量傳送出去，例如whatsapp給所有contact，瘋狂air drop給路人。另外，希望大家能主動列印文宣，貼在不同地方，務求令香港人一見到🖐☝️黃金周，就會聯想起五大訴求 缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n至於國際戰線，主平台將會是twitter，Reddit等平台。希望大家能在這些平台發佈和retweet🖐☝️黃金周的文宣，並向世界宣傳什麼是 5 demands Not 1 less。再者，宜家twitter戰線係 #nnevvy 事件下，我地香港人同泰國人台灣人都統一陣線。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望能以 #5DN1L #5DemandsNot1Less 等hashtags (只是初步建議)，令更多人關注香港局勢。<br />\n<br />\n而牆內戰線。因為 五一在中国是極度敏感的，好似之前余文樂喺自家品牌度出現 五一手勢，已經激發一眾中国人嘅玻璃心。我覺得我地可以多加利用呢方面，瘋狂將五一黃金週和 🖐☝️黃金周、五大訴求 缺一不可、5 demands Not 1 less等字眼連上關係。令五一黃金週在中国變成禁語。<br />\n<br />\n主辦平台(排名不分先後):<br />\n<br />\n🖐☝黃金週活動Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKGoldenWeek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKGoldenWeek&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=fc4d8d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKGoldenWeek</a><br />\n<br />\n香城online<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/GloryHKGOnline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FGloryHKGOnline&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=b9c48c27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/GloryHKGOnline</a><br />\n<br />\n終極黃藍地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/yellowshoppromotion\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyellowshoppromotion&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=613e153c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/yellowshoppromotion</a><br />\n<br />\n民間記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=6f59c578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/citizenspresscon</a><br />\n<br />\n香港良心guide<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkshoplist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkshoplist&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6Cjk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=dea70363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkshoplist</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zdnMVF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zdnMVF.png&h=d33752c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ed5mh2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fed5mh2s.jpg&h=646845dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWxf64Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWxf64Y.jpg&h=117a2266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4SzNiT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4SzNiT.jpg&h=709b9991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3a4uBci.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3a4uBci.jpg&h=f933f4ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55d85d2fc3fd5033a382d21c0dbc8f43d4fac2c9","tid":1984573,"uid":292926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:04:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f382030c574aa5c1fb7c91e0f3b692dea993aeba","tid":1984573,"uid":11870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"FiveDemandsWeek<br />\nHKGoldenWeek"},{"pid":"cf80c9c428135023fe6d32e89450e010cf171a65","tid":1984573,"uid":292926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"b3952408194a3a1f2d285c5d7749b7697c1cc7e4","tid":1984573,"uid":292926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"推呀！！！！"},{"pid":"015c5ae3132a50c07dcc2cada569ec3c2dce5d52","tid":1984573,"uid":292926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"上熱門"},{"pid":"203da26fa02b6d6779b5a21729091ea43d976cb2","tid":1984573,"uid":87901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:05:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d958a5ff50e789e76323e794c3a8e09d8b12e24b","tid":1984573,"uid":87901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"51<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64be8d0f730cc817450fe7ba4aa04a8b72c9e1a9","tid":1984573,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5b82cb3e6365b3c9cdbd75eddb7a037e4c06e6","tid":1984573,"uid":294153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0